        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK21">
<l>oḻukkattu nīttār perumai viḻuppattu</l>
<l>vēṇṭum paṉuvaṟ ṟuṇivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The end and aim of all treatise is to extol beyond all other excellence, the greatness of those who, while abiding in the rule of conduct peculiar to their state, have abandoned all desire.</l>
            </lg>
